  <p>Hi, you have a new story, created by Jonathan Fagg for the Just Play=
 project!</p>


<p>Tabs should be: =E2=80=98Reminder=E2=80=99 and =E2=80=98Pending charge=
=E2=80=99</p>
<p><strong>Reminder:</strong> Display all teams that have =E2=80=98send_d=
ate=E2=80=99 in the future (+14 days).</p>
<p><strong>Pending charge:</strong> All teams that have a =E2=80=98send_d=
ate=E2=80=99 in the past and before =E2=80=98CL_renewal_date=E2=80=99</p>=

<p>The =E2=80=98send_date=E2=80=99 and =E2=80=98renewal_date=E2=80=99 sho=
uld be based on the specific =E2=80=98time=E2=80=99</p>
<p><strong>Example:</strong></p>
<p>A team has a =E2=80=98send_date=E2=80=99 of 2nd August and =E2=80=98CL=
_renewal_date=E2=80=99 of 8th Aug =E2=80=A6this means the reminder email =
is sent at 11am Melbourne time. So at 11:01am, the =E2=80=98send_date=E2=80=
=99 will no longer be in the future so the team should not appear in the =
=E2=80=98Reminder=E2=80=99 tab</p>
<p>At Aug 2nd 11:01am, the =E2=80=98send_date=E2=80=99 is in the past and=
 it is before the =E2=80=98CL_renewal_date=E2=80=99=E2=80=A6this means th=
e team should appear in =E2=80=98Pending_charge=E2=80=99 tab</p>
<p>At Aug 8th 11:01am, the =E2=80=98CL_renewal_date=E2=80=99 is in the pa=
st so teams will no longer display in the =E2=80=98Pending_charge=E2=80=99=
 tab. Any players =E2=80=98unsubscribed=E2=80=99 at this point will start=
 appearing in the =E2=80=98Past renewal=E2=80=99 section.</p>
<p><strong>JF 1/8</strong></p>
<p>- Sent tab has been removed on =E2=80=98Renewal info=E2=80=99 section.=
 This should be returned</p>
<p>- As per above =E2=80=98timing=E2=80=99 description=E2=80=A6the 1st Au=
gust should only display until 11am Melbourne time=E2=80=A6it is currentl=
y 1st August 11pm Melbourne time.</p>
<p><strong>JF 1/8</strong></p>
<p>- In all cases related to the =E2=80=98renewal_send_date=E2=80=99 the =
specific =E2=80=98local=E2=80=99 time should be added to the scope.</p>
<p>They should change state after the =E2=80=98renewal_send_*time*=E2=80=99=
 which is based on 11am in local timezone.</p>
<p>See example below:</p>
<p>It is currently 5:15am on August 2nd in Melbourne timezone.</p>
<p>All the teams are currently displaying on both the =E2=80=98Reminder=E2=
=80=99 and =E2=80=98Pending charge=E2=80=99 tab</p>
<p>In this case all the teams should be in the =E2=80=98Reminder=E2=80=99=
 tab as the reminder is not sent yet. They should move from this tab to t=
he =E2=80=98Pending charge=E2=80=99 tab after they have been =E2=80=98sen=
t=E2=80=99=E2=80=A6which will be 11:01am local time.</p>
<p>A team should only ever display in one of =E2=80=98Reminder=E2=80=99 o=
r =E2=80=98Pending charge=E2=80=99, they should never display in both.</p=
